reviews.review_text: Ourtstanding Sugaree if nothing is said ablot this show overall, the Sugaree is probably the best you will ever hear

This source is the one to listen to You would not think it from a quick sampling of the available sources, but this is the only source that's at the correct speed/pitch. The others are way too fast. Compare the times on various tracks. If you turn this one waaaaay up then it actually doesn't sound too bad. Not much static. Only problem is that the vocals and bass are a little muffled.
